rows.label: tlk46400071_01_msg0001
rows.name:
This is the main entrance
to Goth Isut, capital of
the Holy See of Acedia.

rows.label: tlk46400071_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Ascend the steps you see before
you to reach Seoris Plaza.

rows.label: tlk46400071_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Beyond the plaza lies the cathedral,
where His Holiness Marveni himself
offers prayers every day.
